<div class="text-center container py-5">
  <p class="cover-heading">You can save <span class="lives">lives</span>. </p>
  <p class="cover-lead">
    Millions of volunteers are needed to help tackle the coronavirus pandemic with less deaths.
  </p>
  <a role="button" class="btn btn-danger btn-lg mt-3 mb-5 shadow" href="#apply">
    Volunteer
  </a>
</div>

<div class="row my-4 mx-0">
  <div class="col-md-2 d-flex text-center justify-content-center">
    <i class="fas fa-hands-helping fa-3x m-auto" style="color: #6c757d;"></i>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-10">
    <p class="cover-lead font-weight-bold">
      <span class="mr-2 align-middle">Help nurses in hospitals</span>
      <span class="badge badge-secondary align-middle">requires immunity</span>
    </p>
    <p>
      Nurses and other hospital staff work 24/7 for months during pandemics. This unsustainable work demand decreseas the quality of medical care and cost lives. Join a group of volunteers at your local hospital to help medical staff. Ease the lives of the heroes of our time.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row my-4 mx-0">
  <div class="col-md-2 d-flex text-center justify-content-center">
    <i class="fas fa-stethoscope fa-3x m-auto" style="color: #6c757d;"></i>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-10">
    <p class="cover-lead font-weight-bold">
      <span class="mr-2 align-middle">Visit patients in home isolation</span>
      <span class="badge badge-secondary align-middle">requires immunity</span>
    </p>
    <p>
      Covid-19 patients with mild symptoms are instructed to treat themselves at home isolation. Most of them are unable to judge their condition and lack the required knowledge not to infect their households. Equip yourself with adequate knowledge, a thermometer and an oximeter to visit patients at their homes. Report the situations of those in critical condition to your community team.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row my-4 mx-0">
  <div class="col-md-2 d-flex text-center justify-content-center">
    <i class="fas fa-baby fa-3x m-auto" style="color: #6c757d;"></i>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-10">
    <p class="cover-lead font-weight-bold">
      <span class="mr-2 align-middle">
        Give care to dependents of healthcare workers
      </span>
    </p>
    <p>
      Many doctors and nurses not only care about their patients, but also their babies or very old parents at home. Take care of healthcare workers dependents by visiting their homes. You will help the workers by allowing them to work longer with higher motivation. We need them and they need you.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row my-4 mx-0">
  <div class="col-md-2 d-flex text-center justify-content-center">
    <i class="fas fa-vial fa-3x m-auto" style="color: #6c757d;"></i>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-10">
    <p class="cover-lead font-weight-bold">
      <span class="mr-2 align-middle">
        Curate academic research for busy doctors
      </span>
    </p>
    <p>
      There are around 140 studies published about Covid-19 everyday. Reviewing these studies are crucial in determining the best treatments. However, the medical doctors in the field are not even able to sleep at their homes. Join our international research team to distill the most recent literature and provide scientificly-proven actionable guidelines for doctors around the world.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row my-4 mx-0">
  <div class="col-md-2 d-flex text-center justify-content-center">
    <i class="fas fa-shopping-basket fa-3x m-auto" style="color: #6c757d;"></i>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-10">
    <p class="cover-lead font-weight-bold">
      <span class="mr-2 align-middle">
        Cater to the needs of the elderly
      </span>
    </p>
    <p>
      Prevent the elderly in your community from this deadly pandemic. Cater to their shopping and service needs with your local community team. Disinfect the products you bring them throughly. Raise their awereness about the pandemic with your know-how from Pandemic Volunteers educational contents.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="offset-md-2 col-md-8 px-0 py-5">
  <div id="apply" class="card shadow">
    <div class="card-header d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between pb-0">
      <div class="cover-lead font-weight-bold">
        <p>Apply for volunteering</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body bg-light">
      <%= simple_form_for @volunteer, url: volunteers_path, method: :post do |f| %>
        <%= f.input :country, collection: CS.countries.map { |c| [c[1], c[0]] }, prompt: "Choose your country", label: false, required: false %>

        <%= f.input :state, collection: [], label: false, input_html: {hidden: true}, required: false %>

        <%= f.input :city, collection: [], label: false, input_html: {hidden: true}, required: false %>

        <%= f.input :name, label: false, required: true, input_html: { required: true } %>

        <%= f.input :email, input_html: { autocomplete: 'email' }, label: false, required: false %>

        <%= f.input :phone, input_html: { autocomplete: 'tel' }, label: false, required: false %>

        <%= f.input :immunity, as: :radio_buttons, checked: 1, required: false %>

        <%= f.input :about, as: :text, required: false %>

        <%= f.button :submit, "Apply for volunteering", class: "btn-danger btn-block btn-lg font-weight-bold shadow" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>  

<%= javascript_pack_tag 'location_selector', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
<%= stylesheet_link_tag "theme" %>